WEBVTT

00:10.600 --> 00:12.000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

01:06.540 --> 01:08.000
[The Eternal Fragrance]

01:08.000 --> 01:11.980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

01:12.020 --> 01:15.140
[Episode 25]

01:17.750 --> 01:18.500
I'm going to decoct medicinal herbs.

01:21.110 --> 01:22.090
Aren't you going to save him?

01:27.600 --> 01:28.730
I can't die yet.

01:30.440 --> 01:32.940
But he values you more than his own life!

01:33.940 --> 01:34.530
And you?

01:37.080 --> 01:39.530
You're just a coward who fears death.

01:39.800 --> 01:40.810
What's wrong with wanting to live?

01:41.800 --> 01:42.810
Don't you want to live?

01:45.270 --> 01:46.580
If you don't even cherish your own life,

01:47.520 --> 01:48.620
what's the point of living?

01:50.940 --> 01:51.530
Yes.

01:53.270 --> 01:55.420
The Flower Fairy willingly gave herself for the Demon Lord.

01:55.880 --> 01:57.420
And yet, life after life,

01:57.800 --> 01:59.340
they still end in the same cycle of death.

01:59.910 --> 02:01.290
The dead go peacefully,

02:01.310 --> 02:02.250
without a care.

02:03.720 --> 02:04.810
But what about the living?

02:08.160 --> 02:09.010
You wouldn't understand.

02:10.750 --> 02:12.900
Watching the most important person die before your eyes

02:14.480 --> 02:15.220
and even

02:16.900 --> 02:18.340
sending them off yourself

02:19.360 --> 02:20.410
is utter despair.

02:25.040 --> 02:26.020
After Lu died,

02:27.320 --> 02:28.570
Xiuyuan barely survived.

02:29.990 --> 02:32.690
With me by his side, we sheltered each other from the storms.

02:33.480 --> 02:34.220
And now,

02:35.710 --> 02:37.340
you want him to devour me?

02:38.590 --> 02:41.090
When he wakes up, how will he live with himself?

02:43.360 --> 02:46.300
I don't know if you want him to live,

02:47.430 --> 02:48.810
or die, or

02:50.320 --> 02:51.370
suffer in between.

02:55.760 --> 02:57.130
I won't let him face any of this.

02:58.080 --> 02:59.570
But this is your fate.

02:59.760 --> 03:00.850
I don't believe in fate!

03:02.110 --> 03:02.970
My master said

03:03.870 --> 03:04.940
nothing in this world

03:04.960 --> 03:06.340
is set in stone or forced.

03:07.110 --> 03:08.090
There is only what I want.

03:08.960 --> 03:10.410
What matters is the choice you make.

03:11.870 --> 03:13.570
I want to stay alive with Xiuyuan,

03:14.480 --> 03:16.020
so I'll find a way for us both

03:16.110 --> 03:17.020
to make it.

03:18.670 --> 03:20.570
What if you can't change it?

03:22.480 --> 03:25.370
If it comes down to it, we'll die together.

03:25.710 --> 03:26.570
No big deal!

03:45.390 --> 03:45.940
Lifei!

03:50.390 --> 03:51.090
You're awake.

03:51.760 --> 03:52.340
What happened

03:53.590 --> 03:54.500
last night?

03:57.670 --> 03:58.410
Nothing.

03:59.480 --> 04:01.370
Drink your medicine. Sit down.

04:02.830 --> 04:04.500
Later, we'll go set up a stone for Master.

04:05.080 --> 04:06.090
He liked to sleep.

04:06.550 --> 04:08.410
Let's pick a spot where the sun shines every day.

04:12.480 --> 04:13.060
Lifei.

04:13.360 --> 04:15.740
Don't overthink. We'll figure things out.

04:16.550 --> 04:17.340
Drink your medicine.

04:22.320 --> 04:22.980
Okay.

04:28.590 --> 04:30.620
You dare drink what this wretch gives you?

04:32.030 --> 04:32.740
Master?

04:34.000 --> 04:36.860
Don't get me started. What have you two done?

04:36.880 --> 04:37.620
Cuixuan

04:37.640 --> 04:39.570
mistook you for demon spies.

04:39.830 --> 04:41.330
He's making us bring you back

04:41.350 --> 04:42.570
to verify your identities.

04:43.230 --> 04:44.570
I'm the one connected to demons,

04:44.790 --> 04:45.500
not Lifei.

04:46.350 --> 04:48.180
Take me instead.

04:48.200 --> 04:48.620
You...!

04:49.030 --> 04:50.540
Guangwei, I'm begging you.

04:50.560 --> 04:52.500
Please don't be angry.

04:52.640 --> 04:53.660
I'm begging you.

04:56.200 --> 04:59.330
Look at Xiuyuan. He is already this sick.

05:00.880 --> 05:03.450
You really think they can get away?

05:08.680 --> 05:10.860
- They... they actually got away.
- You...

05:11.120 --> 05:12.180
Look what you've done!

05:14.470 --> 05:16.010
Then we'll find them again.

05:22.390 --> 05:23.500
There are vines under this cliff.

05:23.640 --> 05:25.540
Go down to Ganhua Realm and wait for me.

05:25.710 --> 05:26.620
I'll draw them off.

05:35.640 --> 05:36.420
What are you doing?

05:47.120 --> 05:49.210
Xiuyuan, don't let the demon take you!

05:49.440 --> 05:50.300
Listen to your master!

05:50.760 --> 05:51.540
Live well.

05:54.390 --> 05:55.210
Lei Xiuyuan!

05:56.030 --> 05:57.420
You self-righteous scumbag!

05:58.080 --> 05:59.810
Why do you always act on your own?

06:00.320 --> 06:01.620
Why do you give up?

06:15.270 --> 06:15.890
Guangwei.

06:16.120 --> 06:17.100
He's the best disciple

06:17.120 --> 06:18.450
you've ever had.

06:19.910 --> 06:21.060
Your own disciple!

06:26.150 --> 06:27.500
Don't be too rough on him.

06:29.440 --> 06:30.500
I'll go find my disciple.

06:31.440 --> 06:34.300
Lifei! Lifei!

06:36.880 --> 06:37.860
Lifei!

06:39.440 --> 06:40.570
Lifei!

06:42.230 --> 06:45.250
Xiuyuan, you really know demonic arts?

06:45.830 --> 06:46.770
Where did you learn them?

06:47.350 --> 06:50.210
Was it from the Outcast Tomb at White Cliff?

06:50.880 --> 06:53.940
I am an outcast too. From across the sea.

06:54.520 --> 06:55.250
Impossible!

06:55.880 --> 06:59.010
At Chufeng Academy, I probed your spirit root.

06:59.710 --> 07:01.370
You're truly made of flesh and blood.

07:02.000 --> 07:03.300
Master, you've never crossed the sea.

07:04.320 --> 07:07.060
How do you know outcasts don't have flesh and blood?

07:07.230 --> 07:07.810
Shut your mouth!

07:10.350 --> 07:11.860
I've seen those outcasts.

07:12.520 --> 07:14.860
They're all bloodthirsty beasts and demons.

07:15.270 --> 07:16.330
They're not human!

07:19.030 --> 07:21.980
Just because we look and act

07:22.000 --> 07:22.810
differently from you,

07:23.270 --> 07:24.330
we're not human?

07:35.270 --> 07:36.180
Are you telling me

07:38.830 --> 07:41.130
that the one I poured my heart into teaching

07:41.910 --> 07:44.060
is the very enemy the Central Plains sects

07:44.640 --> 07:46.860
despise most?

07:47.680 --> 07:48.330
Master.

08:01.320 --> 08:04.130
But the way of the world dictates that the rigid breaks first.

08:04.680 --> 08:06.250
Only Wuyue Court's techniques

08:06.960 --> 08:09.540
balance rigidity with flexibility. And that is what lasts.

08:10.390 --> 08:11.660
Would you like to join Wuyue Court?

08:13.080 --> 08:13.860
Yes.

08:16.910 --> 08:19.740
The rigid breaks first. Balance rigidity with flexibility.

08:20.710 --> 08:23.450
Master, thank you for taking me in and teaching me.

08:24.880 --> 08:26.100
I will never forget it.

08:32.760 --> 08:37.690
I'm a terrible disciple. Please take back your gift, Master.

08:41.960 --> 08:43.850
You were taught by me.

08:44.920 --> 08:48.060
I can't let you become a great threat to the immortal sects!

08:58.830 --> 08:59.730
Master.

09:11.280 --> 09:12.180
Master.

09:27.540 --> 09:28.540
Master.

09:43.230 --> 09:45.140
You... Soul bewitching?

10:08.420 --> 10:12.450
Sir, thank you for helping the Lord sever his worldly ties

10:12.990 --> 10:14.140
and return to our clan.

10:14.470 --> 10:15.540
Lifei!

10:18.180 --> 10:20.020
Guangwei, I couldn't find Lifei.

10:25.300 --> 10:26.020
Where's Xiuyuan?

10:42.830 --> 10:43.660
No response.

10:44.920 --> 10:45.810
He should be fine.

10:59.990 --> 11:01.330
What is Qingcheng to you?

11:04.980 --> 11:08.180
At East Sea's Mount Man, the vast ocean stretches endlessly.

11:08.830 --> 11:11.810
Left together by Qingcheng of Wuyue Court and Riyan of Qingqiu.

11:20.750 --> 11:21.780
So my master

11:23.060 --> 11:24.210
is Qingcheng.

11:46.470 --> 11:50.060
The Demon Lord was fierce and unstoppable with the Divine Tree's power.

11:51.100 --> 11:52.730
With my friend Riyan's help,

11:53.230 --> 11:55.730
I severed his horns and dealt a heavy blow to his forces.

12:08.060 --> 12:10.240
I used the Senluo Grand Art to stop the Demon Lord

12:10.240 --> 12:11.180
from destroying the Divine Tree.

12:11.470 --> 12:12.940
But Yecha reverted to an infant form.

12:13.230 --> 12:15.090
Only a faint trace of the Divine Tree's fruit remained.

12:15.300 --> 12:18.180
Yet even a blade of grass deserves life. I resolved to devote my life

12:18.420 --> 12:22.180
to studying this being and finding a solution to the Sea Calamity.

12:33.750 --> 12:34.780
For a century after that,

12:35.040 --> 12:37.140
Riyan and I traveled across countless lands,

12:37.400 --> 12:39.450
but never discovered the source of the Sea Calamity.

12:39.660 --> 12:41.210
Because the spirit energy across the sea is thin,

12:41.440 --> 12:43.140
Yecha's green fruit couldn't grow.

12:43.440 --> 12:45.540
And we were badly wounded from our battle with Yecha,

12:45.830 --> 12:48.140
and our cultivation had greatly diminished.

12:48.470 --> 12:49.570
So we returned to the Central Plains

12:49.750 --> 12:52.850
and went into seclusion in Riyan's homeland, Qingqiu.

14:28.470 --> 14:29.540
Decades later,

14:29.870 --> 14:32.260
the fruit that had remained unchanged finally awakened into a spirit.

14:32.750 --> 14:34.420
Even the Ganhua Realm, with its ordinary spirit energy,

14:34.750 --> 14:36.420
was enriched by it.

14:36.870 --> 14:39.330
After more than 300 years in Qingqiu,

14:39.680 --> 14:41.810
on the twenty-fifth day of the twelfth month in the Year of Gengwu, at midnight,

14:42.110 --> 14:44.900
the shell suddenly cracked open, and inside was a newborn girl.

14:45.280 --> 14:47.900
Radiant and naturally gifted.

14:48.510 --> 14:50.780
She was human, and yet not human.

15:05.870 --> 15:07.140
This girl was born of heaven itself.

15:08.100 --> 15:10.540
Her own spirit energy could generate endless spirit energy.

15:11.630 --> 15:13.540
She could also absorb the spirit energy of others.

15:14.230 --> 15:15.210
If used well,

15:16.510 --> 15:18.420
she could help us boost our cultivation

15:18.990 --> 15:20.210
and make us invincible.

15:22.820 --> 15:26.300
But this reborn Divine Tree was no different from a mortal child.

15:27.220 --> 15:28.730
To keep her from falling back into calamity,

15:29.340 --> 15:31.730
I decided to raise her myself.

15:37.340 --> 15:40.940
But Yecha had a peculiar fondness for her, and I feared

15:41.350 --> 15:42.380
old sins would resurface.

15:43.350 --> 15:45.810
So I set three interlocking seals upon her

15:46.100 --> 15:46.970
and sent her away.

15:47.590 --> 15:48.850
With these seals,

15:49.700 --> 15:50.900
they would hold each other in check.

15:51.230 --> 15:53.970
If kept apart in this life, they could break free from fate.

15:54.710 --> 15:55.690
It's foolproof.

15:57.420 --> 16:00.140
Forget the past. Stay away from conflict.

16:01.820 --> 16:03.570
Just live as an ordinary person.

16:23.590 --> 16:25.690
Mr. Lei of Gaolu was a dear friend of mine.

16:26.580 --> 16:28.330
I set up a protective formation for Gaolu,

16:28.830 --> 16:31.420
and he promised to keep this child safe.

16:45.060 --> 16:46.940
But I grow old, and my strength fades.

16:47.940 --> 16:49.730
Time passes and never returns.

16:50.830 --> 16:52.810
Though I may live long as an immortal,

16:53.220 --> 16:54.690
I long to return to my homeland.

16:55.340 --> 16:56.970
Cultivation is hindered by worldly attachments.

16:57.420 --> 16:59.060
You're meant to rise above mortal ties

16:59.230 --> 17:00.180
and achieve the Great Dao.

17:00.980 --> 17:03.610
Yet now you're held captive by this being.

17:04.110 --> 17:05.810
You've cared for her so painstakingly.

17:06.300 --> 17:07.140
You're seeing her

17:07.180 --> 17:08.660
as a real person.

17:09.220 --> 17:09.770
Do you really

17:10.360 --> 17:12.580
want her to live as an ordinary person forever?

17:15.270 --> 17:16.730
What's wrong with being ordinary?

17:17.120 --> 17:18.580
My Xiaobangchui is so lovely.

17:19.070 --> 17:20.380
Even if she can do nothing, it doesn't matter.

17:20.420 --> 17:21.660
I'll protect you. Right?

17:21.750 --> 17:22.940
Your Xiaobangchui?

17:23.310 --> 17:24.770
You know that no matter how human she seems,

17:24.940 --> 17:26.690
she's still just the Fruit of the Divine Tree.

17:26.900 --> 17:28.730
I've placed seals in her sea of mind.

17:29.270 --> 17:30.100
If you don't tell her,

17:30.750 --> 17:31.970
she'll never know.

17:32.220 --> 17:32.690
You...!

17:34.700 --> 17:35.730
Stubborn.

17:36.550 --> 17:37.290
Fool.

17:38.750 --> 17:40.290
What good is brilliance and talent?

17:40.790 --> 17:41.730
In the end,

17:42.360 --> 17:44.100
you're still tied down by this burden.

17:44.700 --> 17:45.970
You can hide it from her for a day, a year,

17:45.990 --> 17:46.770
even a century,

17:47.220 --> 17:49.010
but how can you hide it from her for a lifetime?

17:49.420 --> 17:50.420
As long as I live,

17:51.420 --> 17:52.530
I'll protect her.

17:54.940 --> 17:55.820
My mind is made up.

17:56.620 --> 17:57.580
Don't try to change it.

18:07.900 --> 18:09.580
I used to live on Hushe Peak.

18:09.940 --> 18:11.290
Everyone said it looked like a mallet.

18:11.620 --> 18:12.250
You

18:12.660 --> 18:14.100
are Xiaobangchui.
[*Sounds like "little mallet"]

18:21.220 --> 18:22.770
The Divine Tree brims with natural spirit energy.

18:23.230 --> 18:24.420
Without external spirit energy input,

18:24.940 --> 18:26.250
it draws out spirit energy on its own.

18:27.030 --> 18:30.340
The spirits around Qingqiu were all drawn to it and purified.

18:36.710 --> 18:37.450
Don't be afraid.

18:37.700 --> 18:38.530
But when she was three,

18:38.990 --> 18:40.100
a calamity struck,

18:40.220 --> 18:42.180
and her innate spirit energy suddenly vanished.

18:42.310 --> 18:44.140
She became no different from an ordinary child,

18:44.470 --> 18:45.770
unable to channel any spirit energy.

18:46.510 --> 18:47.530
All these peculiarities

18:47.620 --> 18:49.770
were hidden within this ordinary girl.

18:49.940 --> 18:51.860
Since I treated the child as my own,

18:51.900 --> 18:53.210
Riyan worried my attachments

18:53.470 --> 18:54.770
would block my cultivation recovery.

18:55.230 --> 18:57.580
He repeatedly urged me to teach her the way of cultivation.

18:57.710 --> 18:58.860
I always refused.

18:58.990 --> 18:59.730
In a fit of anger,

19:00.030 --> 19:01.730
Riyan left Qingqiu.

19:09.460 --> 19:10.620
It's fine if you can't do it.

19:11.230 --> 19:13.420
You could just be my disciple.

19:13.750 --> 19:14.820
A girl

19:14.860 --> 19:17.490
spending her days fighting isn't proper.

19:18.470 --> 19:20.420
Making braised radish for me

19:20.460 --> 19:21.210
is the real business.

19:21.310 --> 19:21.970
Am I right?

19:22.700 --> 19:24.380
I'm dirt poor.

19:24.620 --> 19:26.010
If I raised you like a proper girl,

19:26.700 --> 19:28.100
we'd starve.

19:30.270 --> 19:30.900
Let's go.

19:31.790 --> 19:34.180
We'll go make some money.

19:34.180 --> 19:37.500
[Infallible Divination]

19:37.510 --> 19:38.420
Let's go!

19:38.460 --> 19:39.450
Sir, I'll have a baozi.

19:39.470 --> 19:39.940
Sure.

19:39.980 --> 19:41.050
Xiaobangchui, are you hungry?

19:41.990 --> 19:44.380
I'll buy you something to eat.

19:44.420 --> 19:45.380
Sir, would you like a baozi?

19:45.420 --> 19:46.490
Two, please.

19:46.710 --> 19:47.250
This one.

19:47.790 --> 19:48.290
Here.

19:49.230 --> 19:50.100
This one.

19:51.360 --> 19:52.210
Careful. It's hot.

20:05.840 --> 20:08.970
The girl was clever and sharp. It brought me great comfort.

20:09.600 --> 20:10.730
But all these peculiarities

20:10.960 --> 20:13.140
would make her life restless.

20:13.600 --> 20:15.250
So I gave everything I had

20:15.600 --> 20:17.250
to protect her for life.

20:44.840 --> 20:46.490
I thought if I concealed her spirit aura

20:46.680 --> 20:47.860
and hid her among the mortals,

20:48.340 --> 20:50.010
we'd have nothing to worry about.

20:50.880 --> 20:53.210
But heaven had other plans.

20:54.100 --> 20:55.050
Over a decade later,

20:55.440 --> 20:58.340
she crossed paths with an old enemy she was never meant to see again.

20:59.990 --> 21:01.380
Knowing my cover was blown

21:01.400 --> 21:02.860
and I could no longer protect her,

21:03.340 --> 21:04.620
I quickly sent word to Riyan.

21:05.160 --> 21:07.250
Fearing it was too late, I left a hurried note

21:07.640 --> 21:09.580
for Xiaobangchui to go to Chufeng Academy

21:09.880 --> 21:11.770
and seek my other disciple, Hu Jiaping.

21:12.200 --> 21:13.100
At the academy,

21:13.550 --> 21:15.730
with Jiaping and my old friend Zuo Qiu watching over her,

21:16.200 --> 21:17.970
perhaps she and the Yecha boy

21:18.470 --> 21:19.940
wouldn't repeat the same ill-fated bond.

21:22.920 --> 21:24.450
Master, food's ready.

21:30.070 --> 21:30.690
Master!

21:30.710 --> 21:33.010
I couldn't bear to leave the girl behind.

21:33.510 --> 21:34.250
Master!

21:34.270 --> 21:34.940
But

21:35.270 --> 21:37.250
Cuixuan's tracking talisman had caught up.

21:37.840 --> 21:38.690
Master!

21:51.440 --> 21:52.770
Cuixuan claimed to be severely wounded

21:53.270 --> 21:55.420
and invited me to meet him at Hushe Peak.

21:56.470 --> 21:59.530
I walked into his trap and was captured.

22:12.960 --> 22:13.900
Qingcheng.

22:15.470 --> 22:16.530
Where is the Divine Tree?

22:19.880 --> 22:21.010
There is

22:22.230 --> 22:23.770
no Divine Tree in this world.

22:25.750 --> 22:27.620
As a disciple of Wuyue Court,

22:28.200 --> 22:29.770
you side with those across the sea

22:30.070 --> 22:31.250
and cozy up to monsters.

22:31.550 --> 22:33.010
You even built the Outcast Tomb.

22:33.440 --> 22:34.100
Tell me,

22:34.710 --> 22:36.860
where have you hidden the Divine Tree?

22:43.200 --> 22:46.770
In this life, I was tied down by worldly attachments

22:47.070 --> 22:48.290
and never achieved the Great Dao.

22:48.840 --> 22:52.420
My only wish is that Xiaobangchui can live as an ordinary person,

22:53.230 --> 22:54.450
[Senluo Grand Art]
happy and free

22:54.790 --> 22:56.380
for all her days.

22:57.640 --> 22:58.450
Master,

23:00.440 --> 23:01.380
with you gone,

23:02.990 --> 23:04.290
how can I be happy?

23:12.070 --> 23:13.250
Without killing Cuixuan,

23:14.710 --> 23:16.340
I don't deserve freedom.

23:21.400 --> 23:23.010
I want supreme power.

23:24.750 --> 23:26.250
I don't want my loved ones

23:26.440 --> 23:27.900
dying in front of me again.

23:31.310 --> 23:32.050
Master,

23:33.550 --> 23:35.380
I will avenge you.

23:51.790 --> 23:56.290
Follow your will. One thought moves all things.

23:57.200 --> 23:59.450
Scatter into wind, gather into form.

23:59.960 --> 24:01.340
Draw the essence of heaven and earth,

24:01.470 --> 24:04.380
and fuse the five elemental powers of metal, wood, water, fire, and earth.

24:19.620 --> 24:22.450
Let the universe reverse. Let all creation revive.

25:12.920 --> 25:13.660
It's done.

25:30.840 --> 25:31.770
Still not quite there.

25:37.200 --> 25:38.450
With the full strength of our clan,

25:39.340 --> 25:41.860
we'll help the Lord restore his power,

25:42.230 --> 25:45.450
break the curse, and sweep through all immortal sects!

25:51.340 --> 25:55.100
The heart divides yin and yang; a single thought dictates the world.

26:17.840 --> 26:25.690
Save us!

26:25.920 --> 26:26.580
I'm not...

26:27.200 --> 26:27.940
I'm not Yecha!

26:28.990 --> 26:29.860
How can I save you?

26:30.510 --> 26:31.380
Save us, My Lord!

26:31.750 --> 26:34.580
- Save us! - Save us!

27:05.600 --> 27:06.690
Where the heart finds peace,

27:11.550 --> 27:12.580
there is home.

27:14.070 --> 27:15.180
Master Qingcheng?

27:15.880 --> 27:18.100
Resentment is a net, trapping both user and prey.

27:18.470 --> 27:21.010
Only by breaking free can the soul find peace.

27:27.750 --> 27:28.420
Master Qingcheng!

27:34.750 --> 27:35.340
Remember,

27:36.440 --> 27:37.730
where your heart leads

27:38.310 --> 27:40.290
is the right choice for you.

27:45.440 --> 27:46.210
Who am I?

27:47.840 --> 27:48.970
Where is my heart leading?

27:49.200 --> 27:51.900
Xiuyuan. You're Lei Xiuyuan!

28:02.070 --> 28:02.660
Remember,

28:03.440 --> 28:04.690
where your heart leads

28:05.840 --> 28:07.770
is the right choice for you.

28:37.510 --> 28:40.770
Is she wounded and unconscious, or has she gone berserk?

29:00.440 --> 29:01.180
Qin Yangling,

29:01.840 --> 29:03.620
you've been practicing demonic arts just like Zong Quan?

29:05.960 --> 29:07.180
What demonic arts?

29:07.680 --> 29:08.900
As long as it makes me stronger,

29:09.270 --> 29:10.530
who dares say anything?

29:18.200 --> 29:19.140
You can devour spirits too?

29:22.440 --> 29:23.140
Let me go!

29:29.470 --> 29:30.250
Lifei.

29:31.440 --> 29:33.450
Back at Chufeng Academy,

29:33.710 --> 29:35.730
I truly treated you well.

29:44.160 --> 29:45.900
Thank you.

30:13.510 --> 30:14.290
Master.

30:18.030 --> 30:19.100
Cuixuan.

30:19.880 --> 30:20.900
Die!

30:26.920 --> 30:28.140
Overestimating yourself.

30:43.750 --> 30:45.010
You really are the Divine Tree.

30:46.360 --> 30:48.050
You've hidden it well.

30:48.510 --> 30:49.860
You ruined my master's life.

30:50.880 --> 30:52.250
Is the Divine Tree really that important?

30:53.790 --> 30:56.530
With the power of the Divine Tree,

30:56.790 --> 30:58.420
I can unite all the immortal sects.

30:59.510 --> 31:01.340
When the Sea Calamity opens the passage,

31:02.470 --> 31:06.180
I'll conquer the lands across the sea

31:06.790 --> 31:08.820
and wipe out the demon outcasts.

31:09.310 --> 31:11.900
This is the righteous path of the immortal sects.

31:12.120 --> 31:13.100
Righteous path?

31:13.510 --> 31:14.450
It's all nonsense!

31:18.440 --> 31:19.420
What is this?

31:20.310 --> 31:20.900
How is it?

31:21.400 --> 31:25.100
My dragon-trapping lock and spirit-binding seal.

31:25.880 --> 31:26.940
Feels good, doesn't it?

31:27.400 --> 31:29.380
You used these to imprison my master?

31:30.470 --> 31:32.530
You two are truly master and disciple.

31:33.070 --> 31:34.010
Be patient.

31:34.680 --> 31:36.490
I'll make you suffer

31:36.680 --> 31:38.690
everything your master did.

32:01.400 --> 32:02.180
It's useless.

32:03.030 --> 32:07.100
I've fused the powers of the lock and the seal.

32:08.360 --> 32:09.420
No one but me

32:10.160 --> 32:11.450
can undo it.

32:15.640 --> 32:16.620
Cui-Cuixuan,

32:16.990 --> 32:18.450
even if Lifei has done wrong,

32:18.750 --> 32:20.660
we should bring her back to Wuyue Court.

32:21.030 --> 32:22.490
We can question her properly there.

32:22.640 --> 32:23.210
Alright?

32:23.710 --> 32:24.970
The evidence is clear.

32:25.750 --> 32:26.940
What's there to question?

32:30.840 --> 32:32.250
Let go of my disciple!

32:33.270 --> 32:36.050
Chongyi! You dare shield a demon

32:36.070 --> 32:37.770
and defy Wuyue Court's rules?

32:37.960 --> 32:39.210
I stake my life

32:39.470 --> 32:40.620
that Lifei is no demon!

32:42.200 --> 32:43.340
Stubborn fool.

32:44.200 --> 32:44.860
Cuixuan!

32:47.550 --> 32:48.140
Guangwei!

32:54.200 --> 32:55.180
Let's see

32:55.510 --> 32:56.490
who dares take my disciple

32:57.030 --> 32:58.770
while I'm here!

33:04.470 --> 33:05.860
Cuixuan, stop!

33:06.230 --> 33:06.970
Master!

33:10.960 --> 33:11.970
Don't protect me anymore.

33:14.160 --> 33:15.730
I am the Fruit of the Divine Tree.

33:33.510 --> 33:35.580
It was because the Demon Lord possessed the Divine Tree

33:36.200 --> 33:38.820
that the Central Plains sects suffered such devastating losses.

33:39.120 --> 33:41.620
Now the Divine Tree has reappeared.

33:41.680 --> 33:44.730
This thing must not fall into demon hands.

33:48.990 --> 33:50.900
Baifu, watch your words.

33:51.550 --> 33:53.140
What do you mean by "this thing"?

33:53.750 --> 33:55.180
Lifei is a living person.

33:56.160 --> 33:57.380
She's a disciple of Zhuiyu Peak.

34:01.070 --> 34:02.380
You're an elder of Zhuiyu Peak,

34:02.680 --> 34:04.380
yet she's fooled you all this time!

34:05.200 --> 34:07.010
When she absorbed the Achillea Bead,

34:07.310 --> 34:08.450
I found it suspicious.

34:08.600 --> 34:10.820
But you defended her at every turn!

34:12.960 --> 34:14.780
Why bring up

34:14.800 --> 34:16.130
the Achillea Bead again?

34:16.360 --> 34:18.010
Lifei earned that Achillea Bead

34:18.030 --> 34:20.010
fair and square.

34:20.590 --> 34:22.780
Yes, she is the Divine Tree.

34:23.150 --> 34:23.940
But has she ever done

34:23.960 --> 34:26.010
anything harmful?

34:26.720 --> 34:29.420
Has she ever hurt any of the immortal sects?

34:29.590 --> 34:31.610
She colluded with demons, trespassed into the forbidden area,

34:31.840 --> 34:32.650
and wounded Yangling!

34:32.920 --> 34:34.970
Every one of those is a violation!

34:35.400 --> 34:36.090
Besides,

34:37.670 --> 34:39.220
for the immortal sects of the Central Plains,

34:39.670 --> 34:40.780
the existence of the Divine Tree

34:40.800 --> 34:42.010
is a great threat!

34:42.030 --> 34:44.380
You see her as a threat,

34:44.840 --> 34:46.300
so you want to kill her.

34:46.590 --> 34:47.220
Is that it?

34:47.920 --> 34:48.450
And

34:48.880 --> 34:50.300
you said she trespassed into the forbidden area.

34:50.760 --> 34:51.570
I want to know

34:51.960 --> 34:53.700
what exactly is hidden in the forbidden area

34:53.700 --> 34:54.900
of Hushe Peak!

34:55.360 --> 34:58.010
Why did Lifei go to such lengths to break in?

35:08.320 --> 35:09.490
She and Lei Xiuyuan

35:09.700 --> 35:11.450
are both demons from across the sea.

35:11.960 --> 35:12.940
They posed as our disciples

35:13.400 --> 35:15.260
to spy on our sect's secrets.

35:16.960 --> 35:19.450
Chongyi, you should know

35:20.550 --> 35:22.610
that the righteous and the demonic can't coexist.

35:23.280 --> 35:24.700
If you continue to take her side

35:24.720 --> 35:25.700
and blur the lines,

35:25.920 --> 35:28.450
don't blame me for being harsh.

35:29.150 --> 35:29.650
What,

35:30.800 --> 35:33.090
are you going to charge me with colluding with demons too?

35:36.700 --> 35:37.530
Fine.

35:38.030 --> 35:40.490
You've never liked Lifei or me anyway.

35:40.800 --> 35:41.340
Might as well

35:41.880 --> 35:43.610
lock us up together!

35:43.990 --> 35:45.970
That way, you won't have to keep guessing

35:45.990 --> 35:47.340
and finding faults with us!

35:47.630 --> 35:48.090
You...!

35:48.550 --> 35:49.530
Alright.

35:49.550 --> 35:50.420
Don't let an outcast

35:50.440 --> 35:51.530
damage our bonds.

35:52.150 --> 35:53.700
Let's detain the Divine Tree for now.

35:54.070 --> 35:55.450
We'll discuss what to do next.

35:57.700 --> 35:58.900
You're still injured.

35:59.670 --> 36:00.700
Let's not rush into this.

36:01.070 --> 36:02.300
We'll deal with this later.

36:04.920 --> 36:05.780
The Divine Tree has been captured.

36:06.510 --> 36:08.220
The demons won't let this rest.

36:09.590 --> 36:10.530
We must be on guard.

36:11.360 --> 36:14.450
I've ordered a restriction spell over Wuyue Shrine

36:14.590 --> 36:15.610
and sealed off all news.

36:18.440 --> 36:21.530
But while the Divine Tree is detained,

36:21.990 --> 36:22.780
no one

36:23.400 --> 36:24.970
is to approach Wuyue Shrine.

36:29.670 --> 36:30.220
Where's Dongyang?

36:31.760 --> 36:32.530
Where is he?

36:33.110 --> 36:35.570
The day before, Dongyang received a letter from an old friend.

36:36.190 --> 36:37.740
He was invited on urgent business.

36:38.070 --> 36:39.170
He'll be back in a few days.

36:39.190 --> 36:40.570
The sect is in turmoil,

36:40.880 --> 36:42.610
yet he still has the mind for social visits?

36:43.280 --> 36:45.130
You've all gotten too comfortable.

36:45.840 --> 36:46.780
You no longer know what matters!

37:20.700 --> 37:22.940
Lifeng was damaged

37:23.070 --> 37:24.170
and is hard to repair.

37:24.880 --> 37:28.700
For now, all we can do is protect Mu's remaining spirit.

37:29.220 --> 37:31.610
We'll need to find a rare spirit-energy treasure

37:31.960 --> 37:33.900
to reforge her sword body.

37:36.320 --> 37:37.010
Perhaps...

37:37.510 --> 37:38.450
Perhaps what, sir?

37:39.070 --> 37:40.090
You must save Mu.

37:40.360 --> 37:40.940
She...

37:43.190 --> 37:43.820
Jiaping.

37:50.280 --> 37:52.300
Mu is a thousand-year-old artifact spirit.

37:54.070 --> 37:55.300
As long as she has a breath of life,

37:56.150 --> 37:57.450
there's still a chance to mend

37:57.840 --> 37:59.420
her primordial spirit and restore her body.

38:00.470 --> 38:01.420
As for you,

38:02.030 --> 38:03.130
you were wounded by Cuixuan.

38:03.720 --> 38:07.050
Your cultivation has dropped by at least forty percent.

38:08.990 --> 38:10.010
I was careless.

38:11.280 --> 38:13.170
I never expected that Cuixuan's seclusion for healing

38:14.280 --> 38:16.380
was about collecting demon bones in the miniature realm,

38:17.320 --> 38:18.300
absorbing their lingering spirits,

38:18.760 --> 38:19.530
and taking them for himself.

39:23.150 --> 39:23.610
Let's go.

39:25.150 --> 39:29.170
Master Qingcheng was probably murdered.

39:32.320 --> 39:34.610
Sir, I'll leave Mu in your care.

39:36.800 --> 39:37.860
I'm going to Wuyue Court.

39:38.360 --> 39:39.300
For Lifei?

39:39.440 --> 39:39.940
Yes.

39:40.470 --> 39:42.260
Lifei sent me a distant-sensing talisman from Qingqiu.

39:43.220 --> 39:45.130
She's probably been taken back to Wuyue Court by Cuixuan.

39:45.700 --> 39:47.340
Cuixuan has always wanted the Divine Tree all to himself.

39:48.150 --> 39:49.380
Lifei is in grave danger

39:49.550 --> 39:50.700
with him.

39:51.700 --> 39:53.090
I can't stand by and do nothing.

39:57.550 --> 39:59.860
Jiaping, with your injuries,

40:00.240 --> 40:01.740
you won't change a thing.

40:02.860 --> 40:04.010
You'd collapse

40:04.240 --> 40:06.820
before you even saved Lifei.

40:07.340 --> 40:08.260
Even if it kills me,

40:09.550 --> 40:10.900
I must protect Lifei.

40:12.070 --> 40:12.970
I've always known

40:12.990 --> 40:13.940
Lifei's true identity.

40:15.070 --> 40:16.450
But I clung to hope,

40:17.510 --> 40:18.740
choosing to hide and run away.

40:19.460 --> 40:21.300
I failed my master's trust.

40:22.630 --> 40:23.260
Jiaping,

40:24.470 --> 40:27.610
I hope you and Lifei

40:28.150 --> 40:29.860
can live on safely,

40:30.470 --> 40:31.820
unbound by past lives.

40:34.460 --> 40:35.780
Now the demons are running rampant.

40:36.900 --> 40:39.490
The immortal sects are in turmoil.

40:39.940 --> 40:40.940
Outrage is brewing everywhere.

40:41.720 --> 40:43.420
If we reveal the Divine Tree now,

40:44.630 --> 40:45.740
it won't end well.

40:49.510 --> 40:51.700
Since Cuixuan wants the Divine Tree for himself,

40:53.300 --> 40:55.130
let's make the news of its appearance

40:56.110 --> 40:57.380
known to all.

41:04.400 --> 41:04.970
Master,

41:05.240 --> 41:07.130
everyone's saying Lifei colluded with demons

41:07.150 --> 41:08.010
and is an outcast from across the sea.

41:08.940 --> 41:10.220
They're saying she should be tortured.

41:10.590 --> 41:11.530
Is any of it true?

41:15.380 --> 41:19.450
If Lifei really is an outcast,

41:20.670 --> 41:22.700
what will you do?

41:23.110 --> 41:25.340
Master, as long as you still claim her as your disciple,

41:25.630 --> 41:27.130
she'll always be our junior sister.

41:27.460 --> 41:27.940
Yeah.

41:28.300 --> 41:29.820
I trust Lifei's character.

41:30.190 --> 41:31.740
She would never harm the innocent

41:31.780 --> 41:32.900
or bring shame to you.

41:33.550 --> 41:34.610
Let's just break her out.

41:34.980 --> 41:36.170
Get her out first.

41:36.720 --> 41:39.380
With your skills? Break her out?

41:40.630 --> 41:44.420
If a fight breaks out, you'd be lucky to just defend yourselves.

41:44.820 --> 41:46.740
But we can't just sit back and do nothing.

41:47.240 --> 41:48.820
Qin Yangling is guarding Wuyue Shrine.

41:49.340 --> 41:51.010
What if he tries to get revenge?

41:51.670 --> 41:53.050
You're right.

41:54.980 --> 41:57.340
That scoundrel Qin Yangling

41:57.940 --> 41:59.780
is capable of anything.

42:05.420 --> 42:05.970
Master.

42:35.820 --> 42:37.940
On this mission, we must seize the Divine Tree's power

42:38.510 --> 42:39.860
and restore Dizang Sect's glory!

42:42.050 --> 42:42.780
[The Eternal Fragrance]

42:42.780 --> 42:44.560
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

42:57.500 --> 43:01.020
♪The warmth within my arms♪

43:01.180 --> 43:04.700
♪I can no longer hold on to♪

43:04.820 --> 43:08.340
♪In the cold night, how can I♪

43:08.460 --> 43:11.940
♪Keep you warm until sunrise?♪

43:11.940 --> 43:15.580
♪My heartbeat freezes♪

43:15.980 --> 43:19.260
♪I can no longer tell you♪

43:19.380 --> 43:22.900
♪Looking you in the eyes, I cannot♪

43:22.940 --> 43:25.940
♪Utter that line♪

43:26.100 --> 43:28.140
♪Knowing love and hate♪

43:28.220 --> 43:32.620
♪Pain and wounds cannot be stopped♪

43:33.340 --> 43:35.420
♪I still linger on♪

43:35.580 --> 43:39.860
♪Unwilling to let go of every inch of our past♪

43:40.020 --> 43:44.540
♪Last night's stars cast faint glimmers♪

43:44.620 --> 43:48.140
♪But we thought nothing of it♪

43:48.220 --> 43:51.660
♪With a heartbroken cry♪

43:51.940 --> 43:55.180
♪I wish you well♪

43:55.340 --> 43:57.060
♪Knowing right and wrong♪

43:57.220 --> 44:01.900
♪Black and gray are all illusions♪

44:02.500 --> 44:04.580
♪You're still screaming♪

44:04.740 --> 44:09.220
♪Running relentlessly without regret♪

44:09.340 --> 44:13.820
♪The storm looms, yet the wind stands in its way♪

44:14.060 --> 44:17.020
♪A final farewell left on the cliff♪

44:17.140 --> 44:19.020
♪Leaping straight into♪

44:19.140 --> 44:23.900
♪That heartbreaking past♪

44:24.140 --> 44:27.660
♪Just to keep you safe♪

44:34.100 --> 44:37.420
♪My breath is about to stop♪

44:37.540 --> 44:41.060
♪Those hands can no longer hold yours♪

44:41.180 --> 44:44.620
♪Through the future snow, wind, and fog♪

44:44.780 --> 44:47.980
♪Who will be there by your side?♪

44:48.100 --> 44:51.820
♪I smile as it ends♪

44:51.980 --> 44:55.620
♪Afraid that you might cry for me♪

44:55.820 --> 44:59.220
♪Quietly, I turn into a sky lantern♪

44:59.380 --> 45:02.500
♪To light your way through the night♪

45:02.580 --> 45:04.620
♪Knowing love and hate♪

45:04.700 --> 45:09.100
♪Pain and wounds cannot be stopped♪

45:09.860 --> 45:11.900
♪I still linger on♪

45:12.060 --> 45:16.340
♪Unwilling to let go of every inch of our past♪

45:16.500 --> 45:21.020
♪The storm looms, yet I stand in its way♪

45:21.100 --> 45:24.300
♪Torn inside, still I burn bright♪

45:24.500 --> 45:26.460
♪With the light from my fingertips♪

45:26.540 --> 45:30.940
♪I build a paradise♪

45:31.100 --> 45:34.580
♪To wander with you♪
